4. Joy
   - Character: Captain Bildad
   - Intensity: 0.6
   - Cause: Wishing the crew well on their voyage
   - Object: Crew and ship
   - Place: On the ship
   - Quote: "‘God bless ye, and have ye in His holy keeping, men,’ murmured old Bildad, almost incoherently. ‘I hope ye’ll have fine weather now, so that Captain Ahab may soon be moving among ye—a pleasant sun is all he needs, and ye’ll have plenty of them in the tropic voyage ye go."

5. Anticipation
   - Character: Captain Peleg
   - Intensity: 0.7
